  "detailed_description": "<h1>Kinect connection tip!</h1><p>Place Kinect at a distance of 2 meters to 3 meters and a height of 1 meter for smooth play.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/796970/extras/Set_Kinect.PNG?t=1522655564\" /></span></p><br><h1>UI selection tip!</h1><p>You can choose by looking at User Interface.</p><br><h1>KeyBoard Input</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Select Game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1 : FreeKick<br></li><li>2 : GoalKeeper<br></li><li>3 : TargetShooting</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Select Level</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1 : Easy<br></li><li>2 : Nomal<br></li><li>3 : Hard</li></ul><br>Q : Skip Notice<br>X : Exit Game<br>C : Continue Game</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Welcome to VrSoccer Training!</strong><br><br>VR Soccer Training is goalkeeper, free kit and target shooting.<br><br>Defense your goal, score a goal, hit your targets and score!<br><br>♪ That's it! ♪",
